data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Back on the market. Buyer’s funding fell through. Seller is willing to purchase credits to lower the buyer’s interest rate and a new roof was installed in 2021! You must see this gorgeous south Lakeland pool home located in the tucked away community of Englelake. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts an eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar, updated appliances, a formal dining room, a brick wood-burning fireplace, french doors, crown molding, hardwood floors, chair railing, and wainscoting. The spacious master suite includes a large bathroom with a jacuzzi tub, a separate shower stall, dual sinks, and a large walk-in closet. There is a beautiful downstairs den/office with custom wood built-ins including; a desk, shelves, cabinetry, and a murphy bed for an additional sleeping area. The property sits on a quiet cul-de-sac with a large .34 acre lot, fenced backyard, shady oak trees, and a playhouse. Enjoy relaxing and entertaining in the screen enclosed pool area that includes an outdoor kitchen with a built-in grill, sink, refrigerator, cabinets, drawers, and a bar. A new roof was installed in 2021. The seller is willing to purchase credits to lower the buyer’s interest rate. This home is conveniently located to several parks, restaurants, shopping centers, grocery stores, and the Polk Parkway for easy commutes to Tampa and Orlando. Call today to set up your private showing!
